And when I go to school, I used to have school dinners.

00:44:34.040 --> 00:44:36.040
I used to like some of the puddings over there.

00:44:37.040 --> 00:44:39.040
Sponge pudding and things like that with custard.

00:44:39.040 --> 00:44:40.040
I used to like that.

00:44:41.040 --> 00:44:43.040
But most of the dinners, I mean,

00:44:44.040 --> 00:44:46.040
I would eat a little bit.

00:44:47.040 --> 00:44:54.040
But I wouldn't finish it because some of them you have to add salt to it.

00:44:55.040 --> 00:44:58.040
I said no, I said you're supposed to cook with salt.

00:44:59.040 --> 00:45:02.040
When you cook with salt, everything goes in it.

00:45:02.040 --> 00:45:06.040
Only salt goes in the food because you put the salt in the water.

00:45:06.040 --> 00:45:08.040
So the water cooks the food, so everything goes in there.

00:45:09.040 --> 00:45:11.040
But you have to add salt to it.

00:45:11.040 --> 00:45:13.040
I didn't see the sense in that.

00:45:17.040 --> 00:45:19.040
I just didn't see the sense in that.

