Do you ever eat sugar cane?

00:47:26.040 --> 00:47:27.040
Do you eat sugar cane?

00:47:29.040 --> 00:47:32.040
Well, we've got some, they call it the governor cane.

00:47:33.040 --> 00:47:35.040
Which is, you know what I mean?

00:47:36.040 --> 00:47:37.040
It's about that big.

00:47:38.040 --> 00:47:39.040
And it's big.

00:47:40.040 --> 00:47:41.040
But it's not that big.

00:47:41.040 --> 00:47:42.040
It's about that big.

00:47:43.040 --> 00:47:44.040
And it's big.

00:47:45.040 --> 00:47:46.040
But it's soft.

00:47:47.040 --> 00:47:49.040
So a joint would be about that long.

00:47:50.040 --> 00:47:52.040
From one joint to the next joint, it's about that long.

00:47:53.040 --> 00:47:54.040
And you only need that.

00:47:55.040 --> 00:47:57.040
If you eat any more, my friend, that wood junkie.

