Especially if it's an extra hot day, that wood junkie will be walking up there.

00:48:08.040 --> 00:48:10.040
And you don't know where he is.

00:48:11.040 --> 00:48:12.040
That wood junkie.

00:48:14.040 --> 00:48:20.040
Especially if you cut it and put it down for about a week, it starts to ferment.

00:48:21.040 --> 00:48:25.040
So you've got a brown stripe all the way through.

00:48:26.040 --> 00:48:29.040
And you eat too much of that, my friend, and you're not going to last long.

00:48:32.040 --> 00:48:33.040
You don't last long.

