I don't care how strong you are, my friend, you would be drunk.

00:48:42.040 --> 00:48:45.040
But that thing will knock you off your feet just like that.

00:48:48.040 --> 00:48:53.040
It's nice, but when you start eating it, my friend, you don't know when to stop.

00:48:54.040 --> 00:48:56.040
And that's the worst part about it.

