I still eat my western dish food.

00:51:13.040 --> 00:51:17.040
I like fish and chips, but curry, something like that.

00:51:18.040 --> 00:51:21.040
No, I prefer the western dish curry.

00:51:22.040 --> 00:51:27.040
I tried the British curry, I said, no, you're saying to me.

00:51:28.040 --> 00:51:30.040
Western dish curry, you can taste it.

00:51:31.040 --> 00:51:34.040
The spice in it and the pepper in it.

00:51:35.040 --> 00:51:38.040
You're eating that and you're drinking water at the same time.

00:51:40.040 --> 00:51:42.040
You're drinking water at the same time.

00:51:43.040 --> 00:51:45.040
I said, no, I said no.

